OpenChoreo GitOps repo profile
Repo path: <abs path>
Pattern: monorepo | multirepo | project-per-repo
Cluster-shared dir: platform-shared/
Namespace dir prefix: namespaces/
Flux entrypoint: flux-system/  (or clusters/<name>/)
Default branch: main
Branch conventions:
  app: release/{component}-{ts}
  platform: platform/{scope}-{ts}
  bulk: bulk-release/{scope}-{ts}
Upstream: github.com/<org>/<repo> | none
Reconciliation interval: 5m
